OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773767470
OL,3,CPodcaster Les Roberts left #20k out of
OL,4,Cpocket after 'cowboy builder' scam
OL,6,FA dad has spoken about being scammed
OL,7,Fby a fraudulent builder who pocketed
OL,8,Fthousands but never completed the work.
OL,10,FLes Roberts was one of 16 people who
OL,11,Fwere hoodwinked by Richard Williams
OL,12,Fwho defrauded them of a total of
OL,13,F#75,840.
OL,15,FWilliams, 53, of Wimbrick Hey,
OL,16,FMoreton, Wirral, was sentenced to 32
OL,17,Fmonths in prison in March 2026.
OL,19,FLes and partner Louise, from Upton,
OL,20,Fnear Chester, asked Williams to carry
OL,21,Fout a loft conversion in February 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
