OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773767470
OL,3,CPodcaster Les Roberts left #20k out of
OL,4,Cpocket after 'cowboy builder' scam
OL,6,FLes, who hosts the Blue Room Everton
OL,7,Fpodcast, said: "Our roof was knackered
OL,8,Fso we thought we'd get a loft
OL,9,Fconversion instead as we could do with
OL,10,Fthe extra room.
OL,12,F"One of my partner's friends had his
OL,13,Fnumber and he came round and said he
OL,14,Fcould do the job."
OL,16,FLes said he and his partner Louise
OL,17,Fpaid at least #20,000 for the work the
OL,18,Fbuilder had promised to complete.
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
