OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773767470
OL,3,CPodcaster Les Roberts left #20k out of
OL,4,Cpocket after 'cowboy builder' scam
OL,6,FHe said: "He seemed really personable,
OL,7,Fyour classic conman who could talk a
OL,8,Fgood game then loses interest. Instead
OL,9,Fof kicking off, we actually wanted to
OL,10,Fkeep him on side because he had our
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,F"For months we'd be trying to be nice,
OL,14,Fwhich feels pathetic in hindsight. It
OL,15,Fcaused a strain on relationships,
OL,16,Fwe're still having to pay off loans we
OL,17,Ftook out.
OL,19,F"We can actually use the room now, but
OL,20,Fit still isn't finished. It's been
OL,21,Fhorrible."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
