PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773767470
OL,3,CPodcaster Les Roberts left #20k out of
OL,4,Cpocket after 'cowboy builder' scam
OL,6,FFor the best part of four years,
OL,7,FWilliams took money from 16 victims
OL,8,Fafter assuring them he would complete
OL,9,Fvarious building jobs.
OL,11,FOnce the majority of the contracted
OL,12,Fprice was paid, Williams would fail to
OL,13,Fshow at the victims' addresses to
OL,14,Fcomplete the work, leaving them with
OL,15,Fincomplete projects which they had to
OL,16,Fhave finished off by a third party
OL,17,Fcontractor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773767470
OL,3,CPodcaster Les Roberts left #20k out of
OL,4,Cpocket after 'cowboy builder' scam
OL,6,FIn some cases, money was taken and no
OL,7,Fwork was done at all. In other cases
OL,8,Fwhat work was done was of poor
OL,9,Fquality, and needed to be removed and
OL,10,Fre-done.
OL,12,F"We had to pay an extra #3,000 because
OL,13,Fhe hadn't stuck the rubber roof down,"
OL,14,FLes said.
OL,16,F"He's terrible at what he's doing."
OL,18,FA GoFundMe has been set up for those
OL,19,Fimpacted by Williams, with an aim of
OL,20,Fraising the #75,000 lost.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@cO]
